des: Owen Caissie grounds into a double play, first baseman Chris Shaw to shortstop Jordan Sprinkle.   Kevin Alcantara out at 2nd.    Owen Caissie out at 1st.
Owen Caissie singles on a line drive to left fielder DJ Gladney.   Luis Verdugo scores.    Pete Crow-Armstrong scores.    Kevin Alcantara to 3rd.
Owen Caissie pops out to shortstop Moises Castillo.
Owen Caissie lines out to center fielder Cristian Pache.
